reviewText: Let a friend view it  ... you know the story  ... never got it back ...
very good movie great picture I wished it was longer great movie I learned a lot from the movie great

The onine info indicated that the video was supplied with subtitles.  That doesn't seem to be the case with Falling Fire.  I already had a copy of the product that was identical to this one, but wanted one with subtitles.
This is the best of both Acts and the Passion, The Last Days of Christ in one DVD. Larnelle Harris's  music video is gripping and will touch your heart. Buy more than one to share with others.
